entries.femaleVariant: <kiroshi l="jpn" o="危険だと警告されたの。オダとも連絡が取れないし、何か変だわ" t="I was alerted of a threat. Oda is not answering. Something isn't right." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="私が参加したのは、あくまでもお父様を追悼するため" t="I only agreed to this to honor the memory of our father." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="操り人形になるためじゃないわ" t="But now I've started to feel like your puppet." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="パレードを中止すれば、弱さを露呈したと思われる" t="If we cancel the celebrations, it will be taken as a sign of weakness." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="弱さ？ 誰の？ あなたの？" t="Weakness? Whose? Yours?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="だが、お前が言うなら中止してもいい。全部やめだ。お前の安全が第一だからな" t="But I understand. One word from you and we can end this, it can all be over. Your safety is most important to me." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="お父様…" t="For father." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="お許しを。どうか、話だけでもお聞きください" t="Please forgive me, Hanako-sama. I only ask that you listen to me." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="サブロウ様は…" t="Your father..." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="父のことを口にしないで！" t="How dare you speak of him?!" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="ハナコ様、無礼を働きたくありません。しかし…" t="Hanako-sama, please. Don't make me do this..." b="" a=""/>
V, run!
Shit! Shit! Shit!
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="兄さん…" t="Yorinobu?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="やり終えましょう" t="We must finish it." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="ありがとう、ハナコ。せっかくの式典だ――やり終えなければ、悔いが残る" t="Thank you, Hanako. It would have been a shame not to finish so heartwarming a ceremony." b="" a=""/>
Thsp…
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="ハナコ様" t="Hanako-sama." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="あなたは…" t="It's you..." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="これが、俺にできる最後のご奉仕なのです" t="This is the last thing I can do for him." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="サブロウ様の死について真実を明かすことが" t="To reveal to you the truth about his death." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="この見せ物では、みんなに役割がある。ミチコは文句を言ってないぞ" t="Everyone has their role to play in this spectacle. Michiko has no problem with that." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="なぜ止まったんだ？" t="Why did you stop?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="俺たちだ" t="Ours." b="" a=""/>
Whatever he did, now we're really fucked!
Hanako's inside.
Tryna call someone, I think.
Try to listen.
Do not forget to disarm the alarms. I must be able to enter.
Goro? All systems jammed. It's now or never.
What is she doing?
Hurry, V!
V, it will be too late soon!
You have no right to keep us here!
On the ground! Everyone!
Go fuck yourself! This is a violation of our civil rights!
Halt!
Does anyone else have anything to say about civil rights?! You can join him!
I almost got trampled... Broken ribs, I think…
We need to get out of here!
I look OK to you? We're about to go live.
Three, two, one...
This is Gillian Jordan of N54 News coming to you live from Japantown, where a commemorative parade in honor of Saburo Arasaka descended into chaos today.
Eyewitnesses we've spoken to described a shootout on one of the celebratory floats. The float in question is said to have been transporting Hanako Arasaka.
Unfortunately, I have no further details to report at this time.
We are still awaiting an official statement from the Arasaka Corporation regarding these events.
Hey! Stay out of the shot!
Ugh, dammit... Let's do it again!
Thank you! People're working here!
As the situation continues to be brought under control, we urge everyone to avoid Kanzaki Street.
Knew we couldn't trust him! What happened to keepin' him on his leash?!
We'd best delta the fuck outta here.
He shot her?!
[Deactivate  security measures]
